es: Elizabeth, no planes no pensarlo, usa la mente que se te dio
en: Elizabeth, don't plan on not thinking about it, use the mind you were given

es: Te cree inteligente, te amo y se que reprimir tus recuerdos a largo plazo no te hara bien eso y lo sabes
en: I created you intelligent, I love you and I know that repressing your long-term memories won't do you any good and you know it.

es: No lo pienses, por experiencia sabes que ignorar las cosas es mejor
en: Don't think about it, from experience you know that ignoring things is better

es: Aunque lo intentes solo te haces un mal, no eres reciliente.
en: Even if you try, you will only do yourself harm, you are not resilient.
